						               													<description>Not long ago, in Happily-ever-after Village , the situation had become extremely complicated, corruption and crime taken over what was a dream city. Laureate storytellers wandered looking for different tricks to survive in this savage world. The city was in deep chaos, every night a new crime took place, a complicated job even for the most suspicious. Are you aiming to solve them?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the game, the players must be divided by teams. One of the first team became the Forensic and will do a story with one card of each category on the table. The players, by teams, will try to solve the Forensic case. At the beginning, the Forensic will provide the name of the case, the victim&amp;rsquo;s name and the time of death.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Starts with the Forensic rival team, the teams will try to solve the case making inquiries about the possible killers, weapons, crime scene and motive. The Forensic will determine how many mistakes have been made in each of the attempts and will reveal different pieces of evidence that can clarify the event.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After several attempts, one of the teams will have solved the case. The winning team will be the one that reaches 12 Points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
